  • Field Details

    • TRANSIENT_ERROR_VALUE_ATTRIBUTE

      public static String TRANSIENT_ERROR_VALUE_ATTRIBUTE
      Attribute that holds the error value that should be rendered instead of the default text property. This attribute will be removed right after the element has been rendered. Usually set by a parent container, e.g. the FormGroupElementModelWriter.

      Given a data-attribute name in case it gets sent to the output anyway.
